        Quokka project
        ===============================================
        
        ### Flask and MongoDB powered CMS
        #### (alpha version, work in progress)
        
        <p align="center">
        <img src="docs/logo.png" alt="quokka cms" />
        </p>
        
        
        Quokka is a flexible content management platform powered by Python, Flask and MongoDB.
        
        
